SNARK is run regularly in
 Macintosh Common Lisp on MacOS
 CMU Common Lisp on Linux
 Allegro Common Lisp on Solaris
and has been run in other Common Lisp systems

(replace "yyyymmdd" by the SNARK version date)

Installing SNARK:

  gunzip snark-yyyymmdd.tar.gz
  tar xof snark-yyyymmdd.tar
  cd snark-yyyymmdd
  lisp
  (load "snark-system.lisp")
  (make-snark-system t)			;t specifies compilation
  (make-snark-system t)			;compile again for more inlining (optional)

Running SNARK:

  lisp
  (load "snark-system.lisp")
  (make-snark-system)
  :
